n a time where food and water are scarce, and seek a smarter way to live. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight fire with fire, and fix what’s broken in this oppressed clockwork city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752780/extras/c3b9dc2cd1a5cd0dd0392113666f379c.poster.avif?t=1755813006\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752780/extras/c3b9dc2cd1a5cd0dd0392113666f379c.webm?t=1755813006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752780/extras/c3b9dc2cd1a5cd0dd0392113666f379c.mp4?t=1755813006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752780/extras/d979058d2df50fd57c8e18349bc4e2c8.avif?t=1755813006\" width=616 height=300 /></span>For questions of help, please join our discord server!</p>",
